Question 2

Vector data: visualise and compare

  1. Make a vector with the following data: 60 85 72 59 37 75 93 7 98 63 41 90 5 17 97. Make a histogram of these data.

  2. Generate 100 random numbers using the r function rnorm(). Hint if you need to know how the function works use ?. Now that you have those 100 numbers make a histogram with these data.

  3. Compare the histogram from question 1 & question 2.
